mash /mæʃ/

(mashing,mashed,mashes) 

1. V-T If you mash food that is solid but soft, you crush it so that it forms a soft mass. 把…捣成糊状 

例： Mash the bananas with a fork. 用叉子把这些香蕉捣成糊。 

2. N-COUNT a soft pulpy mass or consistency 糊状物

